'''Black lilies''' were flowers. They were used in a [[grass painting]] of [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]], but made him look old. He ordered the artwork be burned as a result.<ref name="The Illustrated Star Wars Universe">''[[The Illustrated Star Wars Universe]]''</ref>

